         <div type="translation">
            <p>
                       Left: [Cr]itonia [---]ura, freedwoman of Gnaeus.
                       Right: Publius A[---] Firmus, son of Publius, of the S[---] tribe, soldier of the eleventh praetorian cohort.
                       (He made this while) alive.
                    </p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>
                       Column b, Line 1: "V" in "V(ivit)" is small and raised. Perhaps added later on.
                    </p>
